---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Kids Pottery Painting Class"
  description="Fun pottery painting classes for kids in Centerville, TN. Age-appropriate, safe, and creative experiences for children."
  price="$12-18 per child"
  duration="1-1.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="kids art classes, pottery painting kids, children art activities, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Kids Pottery Painting Class - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Let your kids explore their creativity in our fun, age-appropriate pottery painting classes. Designed specifically for children, our classes provide a safe, welcoming environment where young artists can create beautiful pieces to take home.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Kids select pre-made pottery pieces and paint them with bright, vibrant paints. Our staff guides them through the process, answering questions and encouraging creativity. No mess, no fuss—just pure fun and creativity! Your finished pieces are professionally glazed and kiln-fired.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-made pottery piece selection</li>
      <li>All painting supplies</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Friendly instruction and encouragement</li>
      <li>Safe, fun environment</li>
      <li>Finished piece shipped or picked up</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Age Groups</h3>
    <p>Classes designed for ages 4-12, with activities tailored to developmental stages. Younger kids (4-6) enjoy simpler designs, while older kids (7-12) can create more detailed artwork.</p>

    <h3>Pottery Piece Options</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Dinosaurs and animals</li>
      <li>Dishes and bowls</li>
      <li>Figurines and characters</li>
      <li>Holiday decorations</li>
      <li>Painted tiles</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and piece selection (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Painting instruction and tips (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Kids paint their piece (40-50 minutes)</li>
      <li>Cleanup and wrap-up (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>We handle the glazing and kiln-firing!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Single class: $12-18 per child</li>
      <li>Monthly passes available</li>
      <li>Group rates for schools and organizations</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Enroll your young artist!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"My daughter loved her pottery painting class! She talks about it all the time and her piece is her favorite decoration in her room!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Mom - Jennifer</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The staff was so patient and encouraging with my shy son. He had a breakthrough and was so proud of his creation!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Dad - Marcus</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best way to get kids off screens! Worth the drive from Franklin for this creative experience!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Grandma - Betty</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Family Pottery Painting Experience</h3>
        <p>Multi-generational creative fun with pottery painting for the whole family.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/family-pottery-painting-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Kids Candle Making Class</h3>
        <p>Safe, fun candle-making experiences designed for children.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/kids-candle-making-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint and Pour Pottery Candle</h3>
        <p>Combine pottery painting with candle making for double the creativity.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/paint-and-pour-pottery-candle" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
